text:
â€œSimple, Sorted and Sophisticatedâ€ ye teen Shabd aapke vyaktitiv ko bakhoobi define karte hai Saini Sir. 

Apna first interaction Saini wo ragging ke time hua tha jab tune wo iconic proposal wala dialogue bola tha kasam se mahool bana diya tha bhai. 1st year summer me tumhare group ke saath bakchodiyan karne se leke saath Coordinator banne tak ka safar. 2nd year Takneek me aero club ki trophy saath uthane se leke Takneek conduct karwane tak ka safar. Tere saath serious discusions se leke hardcore party karne tak bhai itni memories banayi hai. Farrukabad ki wo unforgettable train journey. Har ek trip me Travel Guide banne ke liye shukriya mere bhai ğŸ˜‚. â€œChal Kevlin Uth Jaaâ€ har summer ki subah Flying jaane se pehle bhai kya din the yaar wo. Club se hall jaate waqt teri sunayi hui atrangi stories bhai kaafi miss karunga yaar.  Aur aise kitne hi kisse hai bhai apne kaafi shi the yaar wo din. Club me ghanto gaane sunna aur ek dusre ki moj lena sorry sorry sirf tu hi leta tha moj bhai sabki. Teri shayari ke to kya hi kehne meri maan retirment ke baad kavi ban jaa ğŸ˜‚. 

Mere hisaab se you were the most mature individual whom I came across in my campus life. Tere jitna humble aur down to earth aadmi bhi nhi dekha bhai. Bina judge kiye sabhi ki help karna tere se hi sikha hai. IAS banne ke baad yaad karte rahiyo bhai. Aur hamesha aise hi moj lete rehna bhai. Chal kuch kaafi clichÃ© likh ke end karta hun ab.  Thanks for the amazing memories brother. Wishing you all the very best in your future endeavours.

text:
Bhai Amrendra kya hi bolu ab mai tere baare apan 2nd year me dost bane aur bhai aisi dosti hui ki jaise tu mera wingie ho. 

Chal shuruaat se shuru karte hai 1st year summer me tujhse mulaqat hui. Itni khas kuch baat chit nhi hui us time lekin tumhare group ki bakchodi se ye to pata chal gaya tha ki launda chaapu to hai bhai. 2nd year me Takneek ke liye wing visits se leke Takneek jeetne tak ka safar bhai apan ne saath tay kiya hai. Teri wo takneek event me plane udane ki zidd sab yaad hai bhai. Bombay trip ki masti se leke Techkriti ke liye nighouts maarna aur wo tera Tashi ke saath judges se ladna aur phir Neeraj se behes karna bhai tu hamesha se hi honest raha hai bhai sabke saath aise hi rehna yaar. Phir yaar tum sabke support se mera Coordi banna thanks bhai is Kabil samajhne ke liye. Quad and Heli wale project me apan ka Flyer(tu) aur Builder(mai) duo bhai baccho se jyada tu excited rehta tha ki Quad ke liye bhai. Bhai wo tera FPV se stunts maarna mujhse bina puche aur bhai wo tere dangerous Flips. Bombay me quad event mere hagne ke baavajood tera chill attitude. Tera wo peeke ishq me rona saale band karde use yaad karna ab.

Bhai tera doston ke liye unconditional support aur tera never say die attitude mujhe sabse best lagta hai. Chahe kuch bhi ho jaye kabhi na stress lena aur bakiyon ko hamesha  motivate karte rehna kaise kar leta hai bhai. Aise hi rahiyo dost hamesha ekdum unfiltered. Corona khatam hote hi Club trip karte hai. Future me bhi chaapte rahiyo yhi dua hai. Aur ho sake to Gurgaon aa ja.

text:
â€œHaan roo lo tum pehle rooloâ€ iske jaise kitne hi motivating batein aapne booli hai mujhe thanks for solving my stupids doubt of Acads and of my life. Mere Elon musk apne company me mereko naukari de dena ğŸ˜…. Chalo thodi memories yaad karte hain apan ki.

1st Sem ke midsem ke baad ki wo aapki Amul iceream waali treat se leke college se nikalte waqt saath me emotional hona was a hell of a ride. Aapka jab Aeroweek me selection hua tha tab mujhe laga tha kya bakchod bande hai yaar ye ğŸ˜… innocent me. Har ek batti ka course aapke notes ki wajah se hi paas hua hun. EE200 ki endsem se pehle waali raat jab mai paglo ki tarah ghum raha tha aur phir aapne shaant kia tha thodi der room pe padhne diya aur phir bhaaga diya  ğŸ˜…. EE370 ka paper chapwana aapke assignment teepna sab kiya bhai thanks itna help karne ke liye. Intern ke time pata chala aapse patient aur calm banda nhi hai koi ekdum wo kehte hai na aadmi ka asli rang uske bure waqt me pata chalta hai aur maine aapke bure waqt(rarest moment of your life) me aapko dekha hai. 3rd-year Antaragni me saath ghumna aur saare nukkad ki performance dekhna aur har baar China trail me hi khana kaafi epic Antaragni thi yaar wo. Lockdown me jab bhi demotivate hota tha to call pe mere roone dhone ko aaram se sunna aur phir possible options explore karne ke liye motivate karna thanks Sajal being there for me in tough times you are on top of my goto persons list. Meri intern aur meri job sab aapki hi wajah se hai bro kitna bada karz kaise chukaunga bro. Aakhiri dino me badminton khelna, Chaupati ka menu explore karna, aapke saath, aapka mujhe Blackmirror ke liye convince karna aur mera aapko Indian movies ke liye convince karna aur na jaane kitni hi aisi haseen yaadon ke liye shukriya mere ajeez dost Sajal.

Chaapu kehna to aapke personality ko justify hi nhi karta aapne Chappuness ki alag limit set kar di hai. Aapki sabse badhiya baat aapka optimistic aur logical approach hai life ko leke. Aapki modesty aur dusro ki help selflessly karne ke jazbe ko salam mere dost. Aapke jitna perfect maine to nhi dekha yaar puri life me apne. Kosis karna aise hi rehne ka aur Bhabhi ko namaste bolna ğŸ™ğŸ™ğŸ™ğŸ™. Kuch panktiyon se khatam karta hun.

text:
Vedu bro sorry sorry nhi bolunga Vedu. Aapki dosti ko mai is chote se memoir me to nhi bayan kar sakta. Meri dictionary me â€œSimplicityâ€ has been changed to Vedant Kedar aur iske jaise kitne sabdo ki paribhasa aapne change kari hai. Ye 4 saal college ke mai aapke bina imagine nhi kar sakta kuch iss tarah ki apni dosti hai.

Mujhe yaad hai jab hum teeno (Yugesh mai aur Aap) kuch baat karne ke baad sone ja rahe the aur fir aap Stephen King ki â€œShiningâ€ padhne lage mujhe laga bhai kitne awesome hai yaar ye books wagerah padh rahe hai wo bhi course ke bahar ki  ğŸ˜… stupid me. Meri to pehli phone bhi aapne hi order kari hai bro aur yaad hai mujhe aapko maine kitna irritate kar raha tha ki konsa phone loon thanks for tolerating my stupidity. 1st year me aapne to itni saari treat di hai ki koi ginnti nhi hai. Aapko soote hue uthane ki bhi galti ek baar kari hai maine bhai sahab wo aapki darawni look aaj bhi phatt ke haath me aa jaati hai.  Aapke Iphone ki photo kheechna, Hall-10 me lala maggi khana, hamare triple room me sabke saath bulla kaatna, aapse bina puche aapka chweeda khana ğŸ˜… kya nhi kiya bhai apan ne. In sab ke beech ek galti hi hui mere se aapse behas karke us raat ko mai kabhi nhi bhul paunga bhai sorry for my immature stupidity and thanks for forgiving me. Aapke karan mera Aero Club me ghusna us project me kitne maze kare bhai apan ne aapka â€œBarbie Girlâ€ bajana ğŸ˜† aur Neeraj ki jo aapne maari thi kasam se maza aa gaya tha. Apni wo Chicken ki bet pragyan pe mujhe haar karke accha lagta hai ab. 

2nd year me aapke double room pe to itni epic parties kari hai ki koi yaad si nhi aa rahi hai ğŸ˜…. Movie nights se leke patte khelna, aapko youtube pe ajeeb ajeeb videos dikhana. 3rd year me to aapke room pe hi pade rehna sorry aapke personal time me bhi aapko kaafi tang kiya hai. Maal, Daaru sab aapke guidance me try kara hai aur uske aage bhi aapke hi guidance me try karunga Vedant. Trip me aapke saath trekking karna aur kasol explore karna mujhe to lagta hai itni jo awesome meri college life rahi hai wo aapki hi wajah se hai. Last ke kuch dino ki jo epic parties kari matlab maza sa hi aa gaya tha aur us raat jab hum sabhi emotional hue the usko to nhi bhul paunga zindagi bhar. 

Aapke jaisa Open, Simple, Modest aur Cool aadmi milna mushkil hai Vedant. Itna down to Earth aadmi aap eklaute ho Vedant. Ab mere shabd khatam ho gaye hai Vedant. Aur kitni hi taareef karu mai jitni bhi karunga sab kam hi lagega aapke vyaktitiv ke saamne. Sab normal hote hi Trip pe chalte hai baaki December me to Bali chal hi rahe hai. Baaki jaldi se placement lagwaoâ¤ï¸â¤ï¸â¤ï¸â¤ï¸.

text:
Shukla bro 1st-year ki little little interaction se leke 4th year me saath rone tak kaafi yaadein banayi hai bro saath me. 

â€œChalo be Keeevlin kya kar rahe ho basket ball khelne chaloâ€ will never forget bhai matlab jitni bhi basket ball khelne aayi hai mujhe aap logo ke hi wajah se aayi hai. 2nd year me kitni masti ki hai yaar apan ne shayad isilye mai G-MID ka unofficial member hu ğŸ˜…. Aapke paas bahut saare log the campaigning ke liye aapne mujhe chuna thanks bhai mujhpe vishwas karne ke liye. Risk lena wala aur us decision ko shi proof karna koi aap se sikhe aap to matlab â€œRisk hai to Ishq haiâ€ ke brand ambassdor ban gaye ho ğŸ˜†. Bhai wo groww ki PPT ke liye aapko call karna aur eventually aapka usi me place hona ye mai kabhi nhi bhulunga. Aakhiri ke kuch dino me to matlab alag level bonding ho gayi apni. Quarantine me pelke chicken khana bhai matlab alag maze kiye bhai un 7 dino me. Vishal ke room pe subah ki Pav Bhaji raat ko khana bhai kaafi epic tha yaar wo. Aur wo Naman ke baare me discussion karna bhai matlab kya epic tha yaar wo quarantine. Phir hall me bhand hoke bakchodi karna. Aur bhai wo raat to kabhi nhi bhul sakta jab bhand hoke sabhi ro rahe the. Wo Baby Doll pe dance kasam se zeher tha bhai ek dum. 

Jaate jaate aakhiri din bhi kaafi masti ki bro aapke ghar pe IPL dekhna aur Car ride ek dum yaadgar matlab college khatam hone ki BT khatam ho gayi thi. Aapka har waqt explore karte rehne wala attiutde kaafi shi hai bro. Aapko ko maine bas basket ball court pe gussa dekha hai uske bahar ek dum chill. Bhai meri to yhi dua ha ki aap Startup me bhi chaapo IAS officer bhi bano. Bas aise hi rehna bro hamesha jolly mood me. Thanks for all the unforgettable memories. All the best for your future.
author: Kevlin

text:
â€œHard work always pays you offâ€ bhai for me if this quote has any face then it is Vishal Agarwal. I feel very blessed to witness your struggle. Undoubtedly you are the most hardworking individual I have met in my campus life.

Upar kaafi clichÃ© ho gaya na Vishal aukaat se jyada english likh di kya ğŸ˜†. Chalo shuru karte hai ab. 1st year me wo ECO101 ki BT bhai har quiz  ke baad grade calculate karna aur Inferno me aapki wo badminton waali match bhai kasam se vishwaas nhi ho raha tha aap aisa khelte ho. Aur bhai wo Hackathon wala to din kabhi nhi bhulunga bhai matlab ek to aapki modesty ki saara app ka kaam aapne kiya tabhi mujhe team me liya aur bhai aapka self-confidence us din aap judges se jyada sure the ki hum hi jeetenge aur jab Gladiators jeete kasam se feel aa gayi thi. Cut to 2nd year mai raat ko aata hun 4 baje ke karib sabhi wing me so rahe the mai aapka gate knock karta hun aur puchta hun Vishal koi room khali hai kya aur aapne bola â€œsone dena saamne waale room me sojaâ€ ğŸ˜„. Aur bhai uske baad to itni memories banayi hai jo zindagi bhar yaad rahengi. â€œEk cheesy karle bsdkâ€ will never forget bhai. Pizza khate hue Gangs of Wasseypur dekhna, 3rd sem ke baad wo CPI ka graph banane ki discussion karna, MSO203 ke liye saath me nighout maarna kitni saari memories hai bhai. Ericsson intern ke liye wo aapka interview lena kya hi tha yaar wo. IPL nights Bhai matlab true cricket fans. Apan ne bhai Ankhon Dekhi jaisi movie bhi dekhi saath mein. Maine to bhai aapki wo GSOC wale din bhi dekhe hai bhai aap se hi sikha hai hard work ka asli matlab. Intern ke wo BT waale din. Placement ke wo stressful din bhai apan ne saath bitaye hai. Last ke dino me har shaam aapse badminton me haarna, bhand hoke bakchodi karna, nostalgic hona sab kiya bhai college me apan ne. Shukriya bhai itni saari memories ke liye ab samapt karta hun.

Aap bhale hi dekhne se tough aur kam emotional dikhte ho lekin itne din saath rehne ke baad ek cheez to mai keh sakta hun ki aapke andar ek innocent baccha hai. Aapka doston ke liye har waqt saath khade rehna bhut acchi baat lagti hai. Ab isse jyada tarref nhi kar sakta mai. â€œAur bsdk bhul gaye papa koâ€ should not change at any cost. Jaate jaate kuch shabd â€œ Yaari Teri Yaari Chal Maana iss baari Saari meri fikrein Tere aage aake haariâ€. Thanks for all the wonderful memories brother â¤ï¸.
author: Kevlin

text:
Kaha se Suru karun Yugesh aapke saath to itni memories hai. Chalo kosis karta hun.

First day of college hum sabhi Hall 5 quad me wait kar rahe the Rooms ke liye tabhi aapki entry hoti hai aur aapko dekhte hi I was like ye to poster boy hai bhai Patna ka aur phir shaam me jab room me jaata hun to dekhta hun yhi banda mera roomie bhi hai bhai literally Triple Room ka gham compensate ho gaya tha. Abhi bhi yaad hai mujhe jab mera pehla phone aaya tha to aap kitne excited the. Mafia Nights se leke Late Night Oat sessions tak bhai kitni yaadein hai. Theatre me pehli movie (Murder on the Orient express) aapne hi dikhayi thi. Wo aapka Google Pay install karwanağŸ˜‚. ESC101 ke exam din aapki Binary Trees ki class, TA201 exam ke liye saath me ratta maarna. Aapka hamesha motivate karte rehna. Mujpe aapka unconditional trust thanks bhai meant a lot to me. Bhai aapka facebook post jab mai Coordinator bana tha thank you yaar for your unconditional love and affection. Aapke Saath duniya daari ke debates karna. 

Ab jaldi se sum up karta hun warna 2-3 page likh dunga. Intellectual level pe to Kabhi nhi connect kar paya lekin emotional level pe hamesha connect kiya. Aapka hamesha honest suggestion dena whether ki wo accha lage ya kharab aur over the time wo hamesha hi sahi nikalte the. Hamesha aise hi suggestions dete rehna Yugesh. Aap aao na aao mai jarur aa jaunga Switzerland milne.

Bade bhai ki tarah hamesha motivate karne ke liye thanks Rommie.
author: Kevlin
